<%last_sent=@certificate_order.certificate_content.csr.domain_control_validations.last_sent%>
<%= "(TEST)" if @certificate_order.is_test%> SSL Certificate Order Confirmation (#<%=@certificate_order.order.reference_number%>)

Dear <%="#{@ssl_account.reseller.first_name} #{@ssl_account.reseller.last_name}"%>,

The following SSL certificate order has been placed:

Date: <%=@certificate_order.order.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y %T")%>
Reference Number: <%=@certificate_order.order.reference_number%>
Description:
    <%="#{@certificate_order.description} for #{(@certificate_order.certificate_content.csr.common_name)}"%>
<%order_line_items(@certificate_order,true).each do |item|-%>
      - <%=item%>
<%end-%>
      
Order Amount: <%=@certificate_order.price.format%>

Your SSL account has been debited <%=@certificate_order.price.format%>.
If you would prefer the request be sent to a different address, please visit <%=new_certificate_order_validation_url(@certificate_order)%> to change the address.
